me"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The firm had three attorneys and one paralegal. Every attorney tracked time in a spreadsheet, then spent 90 minutes at the end of each month writing matter summaries from memory, drafting invoices in Word, and manually entering line items into QuickBooks. For three attorneys, that's 4.5 hours per billing cycle per attorney — roughly 18 hours total, every single month."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"The paralegal spent another 6 hours reconciling entries and chasing attorneys for missing descriptions. Total monthly billing overhead: ~24 hours. At a blended billing rate of $350/hour, that's $8,400 of attorney time going to admin every month."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[15px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":"The managing partner's goal: cut that to under 2 hours per attorney, without sacrificing billing accuracy or detail."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-14","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-[#c9a84c] mb-5","children":"The Workflow — 4 Steps"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-[22px] font-light text-[#f0ede8] mb-8","children":"Time tracking → AI matter summary → invoice draft → QuickBooks export"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border-b border-[#1e1e1e] px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#c9a84c]","children":"Step 01"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-1 h-1 bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-full"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"Time capture — Toggl Track"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-3","children":"Attorneys use Toggl Track (free tier works). Each time entry gets a client tag and a brief label — \"deposition prep,\" \"contract review,\" \"client call.\" Takes 10 seconds per entry. No summaries written yet."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#5a5550]","children":"Tool: Toggl Track — Free / $10/seat. Alternative: Harvest, Clockify."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border-b border-[#1e1e1e] px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#c9a84c]","children":"Step 02"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-1 h-1 bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-full"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"AI matter summary — Claude via Zapier"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-5","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed mb-3","children":"At month end, a Zapier automation pulls all Toggl entries for each client and sends them to Claude via the Anthropic API. Claude groups entries by matter, writes professional billing descriptions, and returns a formatted matter summary with time subtotals."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[14px] text-[#9a9590] leading-relaxed","children":"The attorney reviews the output — usually takes 5–10 minutes per client instead of 60–90."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#5a5550] mt-3","children":"Tools: Zapier ($20/mo) + Anthropic API (~$8/mo at this volume)"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border border-[#1e1e1e] bg-[#0d0d0d]","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"border-b border-[#1e1e1e] px-5 py-3 flex items-center gap-3","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-[11px] text-[#c9a84c]","children":"Step 03"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"w-1 h-1 bg-[#2a2a2a] rounded-full"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[13px] text-[#f0ede8]","children":"Invoice draft — auto-populated